Package eu.trentorise.opendata.traceprov.dcat

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDcatCatalog
    Models a dcat:catalog http://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-dcat/#class-catalog
    Following properties were not included:
    List datasets and List records
    IDcatCatalogRecord
    Models a dcat:CatalogRecord http://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-dcat/#Class:_Catalog_record If the catalog publisher decides to keep metadata describing its records (i.e. the records containing metadata describing the datasets), dcat:CatalogRecord can be used.
    IDcatDataset
    Models a dcat:Dataset http://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-dcat/#Class:_Dataset
    IDcatDistribution
    Models a dcat:Distribution: http://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-dcat/#Class:_Distribution
    IFoafAgent
    Models a minimal FOAF Agent: http://xmlns.com/foaf/spec/
    ISkosConcept
    Models a SkosConcept: http://www.w3.org/2009/08/skos-reference/skos.html#Concept
    ISkosConceptScheme
    Models a SKOS ConceptScheme: http://www.w3.org/2009/08/skos-reference/skos.html#ConceptScheme
